text: Carolyn Roscoe (born 1966), is a female former diver who competed for Great Britain and England. ==Diving career== Roscoe represented Great Britain at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. She also represented England in both the 3 metres springboard and 10 metres platform events, at the 1986 Commonwealth Games in Edinburgh, Scotland.
